strings: <voice_0x01000C6E><se_high>Tree: It's very strange. I heard him scream all night.
<voice_0x01000C6F><se_high>Tree: He was a very wise and kind king when he was alive.
<voice_0x01000C70><se_high>Tree: Sorry, it doesn't have any value for me.
<voice_0x01000C72><se_low>*: But you have to keep trying. If the king does not wake up, the land will die.
<voice_0x01000C73><se_low>*: ...... I don't know what to do.
<voice_0x01000C74><se_high>Tree: careful! Do you want to meet the king of Askantar?
<voice_0x01000C75><se_high>Tree: It appears he hasn't visited since the Queen's death two years ago.
<voice_0x01000C76><se_high>Tree: He visited me every night. But I don't think you will be allowed in.
<voice_0x01000C77><se_high>Tree: ... It might sound strange, but you'll see for yourself when you come back after dark.
